text: Abigail "Abby" Elliott (born June 16, 1987) is an American actress and comedian. She does impressions of celebrities on television. She played Jeanette Peterson in How I Met Your Mother. She also played Taylor in the 2014 remake movie Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles. Elliott was born in New York City. Her father, Chris Elliott, was on Saturday Night Live in 1994â€“1995.
